This repository contains programs related to Compiler Design and Theory of Computation

The programs can execute/depict the following:
1) File Operations/File Handling
2) Lexical Analysis
3) Converting a Regular Expression to a Non-Deterministic Finite Automata
4) Converting a Non-Deterministic Finite Automata to a Deterministic Finite Automata
5) Shift Reduce Parsing
6) LR(0)
